ibbt.sumo.gui.context
Class ToolboxConfigurationFile

java.lang.Object
  ibbt.sumo.gui.context.ToolboxConfigurationFile

public class ToolboxConfigurationFile
extends java.lang.Object

ToolboxConfigurationFile is created when finish button is clicked. It holds all the informaio selected by the user, and can write this information to 1 or more files, depending what the user wants.

Author:
Sasa Berberovic
